Own A Franchise

Franchise

We seek partners who are willing to share our vision. QBS Franchise Program is unique as it goes beyond the prevalent notions of franchising. What we are looking for is not a franchisee but a partner.

We intend to enter into a symbolic relationship with the individuals who can adopt our philosophy and replicate our business. We are looking for more stores and currently accepting applications for new franchisees interested in multi-unit development opportunities in all over India.

Franchise

  • Salon design & Interior decorations
  • Comprehensive training for staff during start and ongoing basis
  • POS / Billing Software
  • Complete Operations support throughout the term of agreement.

Criteria

We are on the lookout for aspiring entrepreneurs from all walks of life, who are filled with a passion & desire to excel in the rapidly growing beauty & wellness industry. The candidate should be resourceful and should take a keen interest in promoting the brand in his/her capacity.
